                <li>Move cache to durable shared storage for multi-instance hosting.</li>
                <li>Add scheduled index refresh jobs.</li>
                <li>Persist normalized property data in your own read model.</li>
                <li>Add retry, timeout, and circuit-breaker policies around API calls.</li>
                <li>Rotate and protect API tokens.</li>
            </ol>
